<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Computer Learning.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Computer Learning.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Everen Securities said Friday it raised its earnings estimates for Computer Learning Centers Inc for fiscal 1998 to $1.35 a share from $1.30 and for fiscal 1999 to $1.65 from $1.60.</p>
<p>-- It said the increases reflect strong enrollment growth. The company also said recently it expects fourth quarter earnings of $0.29 to $0.31 a share, up from $0.23 a year ago, and above Everen's expectation of $0.27.</p>
<p>-- Everen said it raised its stock price targets to $35 a share from $33 for the six-month period and to $42 from $40 for the 18-month period.</p>
<p>-- Computer Learning was off 1/2 at 31-1/2.</p>
<p>((Reuters Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
